{"prompt": "Generate a website for a financial consulting. The website should be user-friendly and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Elite Financial Consultants</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c62828; /* A strong red */\n            --secondary-color: #e57373; /* A lighter shade of red for accents */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #f5f5f5;\n            --dark-text-color: #333333;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            min-height: 50vh;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            max-width: 800px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .about-section, .contact-section {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .about-section h2, .contact-section h2 {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #cccccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            width: 100%;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form .cta-button {\n            align-self: center;\n            width: auto;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive Design */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n\n            .services-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Using Font Awesome for icons -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Elite Financial Consultants</h1>\n        <p>Your trusted partner for strategic financial planning and growth.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Schedule a Consultation</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Investment Strategies</h3>\n                    <p>Tailored investment plans to maximize your returns and achieve your financial goals.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-coins\"></i>\n                    <h3>Wealth Management</h3>\n                    <p>Comprehensive wealth management solutions for individuals and families.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-calculator\"></i>\n                    <h3>Financial Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Expert guidance on retirement planning, tax strategies, and estate planning.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-handshake\"></i>\n                    <h3>Corporate Finance</h3>\n                    <p>Strategic financial advice and support for businesses of all sizes.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-section\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n                At Elite Financial Consultants, we are dedicated to providing clear, actionable financial advice. Our team of experienced professionals works closely with clients to understand their unique needs and develop customized strategies for financial success. We believe in transparency, integrity, and a client-centric approach to wealth building.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\" class=\"contact-form\" action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"cta-button\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Elite Financial Consultants. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add smooth scrolling for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}